set forth in G.S. 75D-3(7) is deemed to have, have per se violated the provisions of
G.S. 75D-4(a)(1) or (2) as of the date of the second conviction.
(g) Any party is entitled to a jury trial in any action brought under this Chapter."
SECTION 35.(e) This section is effective when it becomes law and applies to actions
or proceedings commenced on or after that date.
