(1) Disclaiming Disclaims any interest in the collateral; andcollateral.
(2) If known to the recipient, providing provides the name and mailing address of
any assignee of or successor to the recipient's interest in the collateral.
(e) Request for accounting or regarding statement of account; no interest in obligation
claimed. – Accounting or Regarding Statement of Account; No Interest in Obligation Claimed.
– A person that receives a request for an accounting or a request regarding a statement of account,
claims no interest in the obligations when it receives the request, and claimed an interest in the
obligations at an earlier time shall comply with the request within 14 days after receipt by sending
to the debtor an authenticated record:a signed record that does both of the following:
