Other Than Debtor. – A secured party having possession of collateral does not relinquish
possession by delivering the collateral to a person other than the debtor or a lessee of the collateral
from the debtor in the ordinary course of the debtor's business if the person was instructed before
the delivery or is instructed contemporaneously with the delivery:delivery to do either of the
following:
