SECTION 81. G.S. 25-9-317 reads as rewritten:
"§ 25-9-317. Interests that take priority over or take free of security interest or agricultural
lien.
(a) Conflicting security interests and rights of lien creditors. – Security Interests and
Rights of Lien Creditors. – A security interest or agricultural lien is subordinate to the rights of:of
